    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(...) + In nomine Domini. Quinto anno principatus domni nostri <persName
                            ref="#people/1913" key="#Princeps">Ademarii</persName>, mense
                        septembrio, septima indictione. Brebe emissa a nos <persName
                            ref="#people/4165" key="#Count">Grimuald</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>, qualiter venerunt nostram presentiam <persName
                            ref="#people/4166" key="#Other_palatine_officer">Madolo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vestararius superius</rs> domni nostri et
                            <name ref="Lupipertus">Lupipertus</name> filius <name ref="Lupus"
                            >Lupi</name> libertus quondam domni <name ref="Audebertus"
                            >Audeperge</name>; tunc ipse Madolus ostedit <emph>brebe sigillatum
                            repetitionis</emph>, quomodo a suprascripta potestate concessa fuissent
                        illi <rs key="#Property_of_persons_without_heirs">omnes res et
                            pertinentia</rs> que fuit <name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name> filio
                            <name ref="Radipertus">Rapperti</name> libertus <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/4164">Hermenaldi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>, qui dicebat esse in <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            ref="#places/2865">loco qui vocatur Lanium, Salernitane
                            finibus</placeName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
